Texts.Eng: A comfortable bench made by the Skath.
Texts.Chs: 一张由绘世者做的舒适的长凳。

Texts.Eng: Ah! Finally, a bench to relax and put my feet up!
Texts.Chs: 啊!！最后，一条长凳让我放松，双脚抬起！

Texts.Eng: Even the Skath want to rest sometimes, and enjoy an ocean view.
Texts.Chs: 即使是绘世者有时也想休息一下，欣赏海景。

Texts.Eng: Floran sssits on waterdragon bench. Becomes sssleepy.
Texts.Chs: 叶族人坐在水龙椅上。变得困倦。

Texts.Eng: Real kelp fabric! How I miss home.
Texts.Chs: 真正的海带面料！我多么想念家。

Texts.Eng: The fabric on this bench is pretty comfy. I wonder what it's made of?
Texts.Chs: 这条长凳上的布料很舒服。我想知道它是什么做的？

Texts.Eng: The kelp fabric used in this bench makes it very comfortable to sit on.
Texts.Chs: 这条长凳上使用的海带织物使坐上去非常舒适。

Texts.Eng: This bench is long and comfy enough to work as a bed! Maybe I could take a little nap...
Texts.Chs: 这条长凳又长又舒服，可以当床用！也许我可以小睡一会儿。。。

Texts.Eng: This'd be a good place to rest my tired ol' legs, if I weren't in such a rush.
Texts.Chs: 如果我不那么匆忙的话，这将是一个休息我疲惫的双腿的好地方。
